snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: The Minish Cap - Nintendo eShop Trailer (Wii U)
snippet.description:
The Legend of Zelda: The Minish Cap is released on Wii U Virtual Console through Nintendo eShop on the 29th of May, 2014.

The Legend of Zelda on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LegendofZeldaUK

Legend of Zelda products on the Nintendo UK Online Store: http://store.nintendo.co.uk/characters/zelda.list

Nintendo UK on Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/NintendoUK
